<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1542,2037]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,298,1722,1748]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459">Habitat.</emphasis>
This species is found in shallow water mostly with dense vegetation, algal growths, logs and other floating debris in lentic habitats (ponds, lakes, swamps and dams) (
<bibRefCitation author="Drake, C. J." box="[921,1059,1759,1785]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="101 - 105" refId="ref48865" refString="Drake, C. J. (1917) A survey of the North American species of Merragata. The Ohio Journal of Science, 17 (4), 101 - 105." type="journal article" year="1917">Drake 1917</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Drake, C. J. &amp; Cobben, R. H." box="[1073,1336,1759,1785]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="35 - 43" refId="ref49135" refString="Drake, C. J. &amp; Cobben, R. H. (1960) The Heteroptera of the Netherlands Antilles. II. Hebridae. Studies on the Fauna of Curacao and other Caribbean Islands, 51, 35 - 43." type="journal article" year="1960">Drake &amp; Cobben 1960</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Bennett, D. V. &amp; Cook, E. F." pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="1 - 59" refId="ref46980" refString="Bennett, D. V. &amp; Cook, E. F. (1981) The semiaquatic Hemiptera of Minnesota (Hemiptera: Heteroptera). Agricultural Experiment Station, University of Minnesota, Technical Bulletin, 332, 1 - 59." type="journal article" year="1981">Bennett &amp; Cook 1981</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Torres, P. L. M. &amp; Mazzucconi, S. A. &amp; Michat, M. C." box="[323,529,1795,1821]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="127 - 153" refId="ref58586" refString="Torres, P. L. M., Mazzucconi, S. A. &amp; Michat, M. C. (2007) Los coleopteros y heteropteros acuaticos del Parque Nacional El Palmar (Provincia de Entre Rios, Argentina): lista faunistica, diversidad y distribucion. Revista de la Sociedad Entomologica Argentina, 66, 127 - 153." type="journal article" year="2007">
Torres 
<emphasis box="[403,461,1795,1821]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="459">et al.</emphasis>
2007
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Munoz Riviaux, S. &amp; Moreira, F. F. F. &amp; Naranjo Lopez, C." box="[542,852,1795,1821]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="1 - 23" refId="ref54309" refString="Munoz Riviaux, S., Moreira, F. F. F. &amp; Naranjo Lopez, C. (2010) Checklist, distribution, and habitat of the semiaquatic and aquatic bugs from Cuba (Hemiptera: Heteroptera: Dipsocoromorpha, Leptopodomorpha, Gerromorpha and Nepomorpha). Zootaxa, 2562 (1), 1 - 23. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 2562.1.1" type="journal article" year="2010">
Muñoz Riviaux 
<emphasis box="[728,786,1795,1821]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="459">et al.</emphasis>
2010
</bibRefCitation>
) and in lotic habitats (streams and rivers) in standing or slow-moving water (
<bibRefCitation author="Drake, C. J. &amp; Cobben, R. H." box="[461,724,1831,1857]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="35 - 43" refId="ref49135" refString="Drake, C. J. &amp; Cobben, R. H. (1960) The Heteroptera of the Netherlands Antilles. II. Hebridae. Studies on the Fauna of Curacao and other Caribbean Islands, 51, 35 - 43." type="journal article" year="1960">Drake &amp; Cobben 1960</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Bennett, D. V. &amp; Cook, E. F." box="[737,991,1831,1857]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="1 - 59" refId="ref46980" refString="Bennett, D. V. &amp; Cook, E. F. (1981) The semiaquatic Hemiptera of Minnesota (Hemiptera: Heteroptera). Agricultural Experiment Station, University of Minnesota, Technical Bulletin, 332, 1 - 59." type="journal article" year="1981">Bennett &amp; Cook 1981</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Torres, P. L. M. &amp; Mazzucconi, S. A. &amp; Michat, M. C." box="[1003,1208,1831,1857]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="127 - 153" refId="ref58586" refString="Torres, P. L. M., Mazzucconi, S. A. &amp; Michat, M. C. (2007) Los coleopteros y heteropteros acuaticos del Parque Nacional El Palmar (Provincia de Entre Rios, Argentina): lista faunistica, diversidad y distribucion. Revista de la Sociedad Entomologica Argentina, 66, 127 - 153." type="journal article" year="2007">
