2007
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Franco, C. L. &amp; Rodrigues, J. M. S. &amp; Azevedo, C. A. S. &amp; Moreira, F. F. F." box="[1221,1431,1831,1857]" pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="551 - 568" refId="ref50573" refString="Franco, C. L., Rodrigues, J. M. S., Azevedo, C. A. S. &amp; Moreira, F. F. F. (2021) Gerromorpha (Insecta, Hemiptera, Heteroptera) from eastern Maranhao state, northeastern Brazil. Check List, 17 (1), 551 - 568. https: // doi. org / 10.15560 / 17.2.551" type="journal article" year="2021">
Franco 
