<bibRefCitation author="Drake, C. J. &amp; Cobben, R. H." pageId="8" pageNumber="459" pagination="35 - 43" refId="ref49135" refString="Drake, C. J. &amp; Cobben, R. H. (1960) The Heteroptera of the Netherlands Antilles. II. Hebridae. Studies on the Fauna of Curacao and other Caribbean Islands, 51, 35 - 43." type="journal article" year="1960">Drake &amp; Cobben 1960</bibRefCitation>
